title: Bobby Doesn’t Get An Invite To Lunchbox’s Dadchelor Party + Eddie’s Questionable Parenting
itunes:title: Bobby Doesn’t Get An Invite To Lunchbox’s Dadchelor Party + Eddie’s Questionable Parenting
description:
Lunchbox is still trying to determine where he plans to have his Dadchelor party, but the invites already went out and Bobby didn’t receive one! Eddie tries to teach his son, who is playing little league, how not to fear being hit by a baseball in a really interesting way. Also, LOCASH and Brandon Ray stop by the studio.
